8 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending Section
16, Chapter 366, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
9 Section 20P), which relates to Class D3 offenses;
modifying list of Class D3 offenses; amending 47 O.S.
10 2021, Section 1151, as last amended by Section 109,
Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
11 1151), which relates to offenses and penalties
enumerated; classifying the knowing display or
12 manufacture of a fictious license plate as a Class D3
offense; and providing an effective date.
13
14
15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 16, Chapter 366, O.S.L.
17 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 20P), is amended to read as
18 follows:
19 Section 20P. A. Upon the effective date of this act, Class D3
20 shall include the following criminal offenses:
21 1. Violation of the Oklahoma Agricultural Code, as provided for
22 in Section 2-18 of Title 2 of the Oklahoma Statutes;
